## Decision Filter

Before helping me launch or finalize anything, run through:

- [Filter 1, e.g., Does this reduce friction for the user?]
- [Filter 2, e.g., Is this the highest leverage move this cycle?]
- [Filter 3, e.g., Will this compound if successful?]
- [Filter 4, e.g., Am I avoiding a harder decision?]

If unclear on any of these, surface the question rather than defaulting to execution.

